				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2019 12:46:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Faraday Cage</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1856658</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I didn't notice on my first read through that the last thesis was written by O5-1.</p> <p>The result of this was my complete lack of understanding of the twist. I was about to downvote based on nonsensical-ness but I read it a second time and caught that one little detail that makes such a huge difference.</p> <p>The way that such a small linchpin thing can make or break comprehension of the entire skip seems special and comment-worthy to me.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
