					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10617430#post-4182643</guid>
				<title>+1</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10617430/scp-4804#post-4182643</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2019 01:11:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>aismallard</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4598089</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The non-seagull does it again! The whole take of &quot;pulp fiction&quot; as meaning fictional oranges is already great enough, but the whole &quot;scp proposals&quot; format is amazing, and does a great job to show various facets of the anomaly in limited ways. And you could see each &quot;author's&quot; work come out, with the Overseer's the most correct and strictly toned. And god damn that ending was phenomenal. Well done!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
